 large T - P range. Moreover it is\nthe first report of a force field allowing to study the transport properties of\nmolten magnesite (MgCO3) and molten dolomite (CaMg(CO3)2).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Apr 2019 09:36:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 15 Apr 2019 13:40:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-26"}
