ed\ncatchment can lead to large improvements in the predictability of runoff.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Apr 2019 12:44:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 7 Aug 2019 09:39:59 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 19 Feb 2020 15:22:21 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 14 Apr 2020 08:37:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-10"}
